dshake`。\n   - 前端服务多次报告HTTP 500 Error，提示来自 `shippingservice` 的错误传递。\n\n### 结论\n- 错误的起始点在于`checkoutservice`与`shippingservice`的交互，多数请求因`timed out`而超时，且这些错误在系统中向上游传播，导致较高的HTTP 500错误率。\n- 延迟的主要瓶颈集中在`checkoutservice-1->shippingservice-2` 调用链上。\n\n### 输出格式\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\", \"error_ratio\", \"frontend->checkoutservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"延迟大幅增加 (17.19 倍)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"multiple 'timed out waiting for server handshake' errors, HTTP 500 errors\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n以上为初步分析结果，请对`shippingservice`进行更详细的检查，以确认根因。", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "70d3b8b0-329", "component": "shippingservice", "reason": "rrt_max spike causing timed out waiting for server handshake", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LoadMetrics(shippingservice)", "observation": "rrt_max increased 17.19 times during fault window, significant delay observed."}, {"step": 2, "action": "LogSearch(shippingservice)", "observation": "Found 'timed out waiting for server handshake' errors consistently in logs."}, {"step": 3, "action": "TraceAnalysis(70d3b8b0-329)", "observation": "checkoutservice-1->shippingservice-2 call chain shown as delayed and error-prone, causing HTTP 500 errors in frontend."}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
